Estee Lauder Nutritious 2-in-1 Foam Cleanser

Brand: Estée Lauder

Category: Facial Cleanser

Ingredients: WaterAquaEau, Myristic Acid, Glycerin, Behenic Acid, Palmitic Acid, Potassium Hydroxide, Sodium Methyl Cocoyl Taurate, Lauric Acid, Stearic Acid, Montmorillonite, Phenoxyethanol, Sodium Benzoate, Butylene Glycol, Glycol Distearate, Potassium S

tearate, Potassium Sorbate, Niacinamide, Sodium Phytate, Lactobacillus Ferment, PORPHYRIDIUM CRUENTUM EXTRACT, Zinc PCA, Sodium Hyaluronate, Polyquaternium-7, Camellia Sinensis (Green Tea) Leaf Extract, Disodium EDTA, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract, Dipotassium Glycyrrhizate, Hydrolyzed Rice Extract, Laminaria Saccharina Extract, Punica G

na Extract, Punica Granatum (Pomegranate) Extract

Directions: As a facial cleanser: AM and PM: Lather and massage over damp face. Rinse. 
 As a weekly deep purifying mask: Apply a thin layer onto skin, focusing on the T-Zone. Leave on 2 minutes. Add water, and gently massage before rinse.
